{"tid":141253,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[夜深改詞] 《除下你皮膚》改 Talking to the moon","createTime":"2017-03-02T18:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:01:13.000Z","uid":40429,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6204e3851dc5bb55db1dbde33199024f1b54489","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"從前有朋友問過我認唔認同「創作就係不停地分裂自已」，當時我以為佢痴咗線，但玩填詞玩咗一年幾，我開始明白呢句說話，我諗我都開始痴線。如是我改咗呢首詞，講緊一個不斷分裂自己又不斷殺死自己嘅人，韻方面嘗試跟返英文詞所以會冇咁公整。<br />\n<br />\n原曲：Bruno Mars 《Talking To The Moon》 <br />\n<br />\n《除下你皮膚》<br />\n改詞：善莫善於水<br />\n<br />\n但我在繼續割捨<br />\n靜待下個你<br />\n拿起碎石<br />\n投出碎石<br />\n<br />\n用唾液證實某些<br />\n愚昩現實哲理<br />\n拿起碎石<br />\n投出碎石<br />\n<br />\n何解不信另外那一半 自己的聲音<br />\n<br />\n除下你皮膚<br />\n除下我皮膚<br />\n剩了是血肉的軀殼<br />\n靈魂與痛苦<br />\n彼此的痛苦<br />\n同樣痛苦<br />\n彼此卻未顧<br />\n<br />\n但我在繼續割捨<br />\n靜看下個你<br />\n來回找碎石<br />\n拿起碎石<br />\n<br />\n用唾液證實某些<br />\n無知世俗道理<br />\n繼續記得驚<br />\n繼續全力掟<br />\n<br />\n何解甘心失去那一半 自己的聲音<br />\n<br />\n除下你皮膚<br />\n除下我皮膚<br />\n剩了是血肉的軀殼<br />\n靈魂與痛苦<br />\n彼此的痛苦<br />\n同樣痛苦<br />\n彼此卻未顧<br />\n<br />\n多少風景遮掩心境<br />\n<br />\n就一次脫下千瘡的肌膚<br />\n就拆下舊城府<br />\n剩了是血肉的軀殼<br />\n靈魂與痛苦<br />\n彼此的痛苦<br />\n同樣痛苦<br />\n彼此卻未顧<br />\n<br />\n但我在繼續割捨<br />\n靜待下個你<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n有創作開嘅朋友，無論係咩類型都好，不妨分享下自己點睇創作呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ecbfe08b95616ded9c37d08c7b0b46f34f53e","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cca32c33da7a870ea7bc8377895fd6825f798f9","tid":141253,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:14:49.000Z","msg":"魚妹燕實哲哩"},{"pid":"1e88d8ab0dd8995d73fef5021791106678aeb586","tid":141253,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"利申：聖葉理諾堂"},{"pid":"b063ce6636f4564a629c87bc5487bf60e0056d7a","tid":141253,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"副歌好有喜感，應該係要嚟搞笑"},{"pid":"20b8872648d03c767f0d8054a33dea2d90f12606","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申：聖葉理諾堂</blockquote><br />\n玄奘大師，我仲以為你係信佛添<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfe400fc4c54cd3249f3f8740122d2543016762","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>副歌好有喜感，應該係要嚟搞笑</blockquote><br />\n竟然係喜感！？<br />\n可否講下點解會有呢種感覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe91c11d1a51736a1405a71b5e3eb8032a7c5fc","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8eb66f9967865e2a3bd804125e80653c7371090","tid":141253,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚妹燕實哲哩</blockquote><br />\n呢句無教會啵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d5efa7d0d0e82b081017d0637945b07257fb5d","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b104c50febe7dbf7f03aa0ea4e6a6303726aed3","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b191ce911bc7bc5f82c8470816db26011a86e039","tid":141253,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaa482378ee4c6